title: Fort Arrack
author: Wolfy2001
pages:
#- Fort Arrack's Story


by Wolfy2001
#- Fort Arrack was founded on 11/11/12 by Poggalogg. By the next month, the population was 19, including:
Poggalogg, JLemer, TutelarySaint2, Rakanne, Kelwyn, zombiesniper57, windsorgriff, pucker678, Rol101, rinscher,
#- Lucky_Leprecon, Undeadh0rr0r, artemisfowlii, Jackan3, Gawdmode, Nicodimasco, 
MonroeZabaleta, Nettrooper, and mjamex.  Soon later, Mandy was caught breaking into the storage, but pucker got her off the wanted list.
#- This was the local map on Dec. 31st: http://i.imgur.com/jjFMj.jpg .  Zombiesniper left town because he was on the HCF wanted list. Soon after, HCF raided the town. Makanla ignited some buildings soon after, but did pay reparations.
#- At this point, Kronstadt had begun. This was a place to evacuate if distaster every struck, such as another HCF attack. The Fort Arrack Grand Canal was finished soon after.  Kronstadt got broken into, and a tunnel conecting Fort Arrack and King's Point 
#- was formed.  Y_ankees then payed a visit to 
Fort Arrack. Afterwards, there was talk of the Fort Arrack "Branches", a council of sorts. Then a proposition for GEaR was made. It would unite several places in the Great Eastern Sea, to make them slightly 
#- formidable.  The town was greifed again by solmem. Fort Arrack was raided by Schtek and saftybear, who soon afterwards greifed it. At this point, Poggalogg quit, with Rakanne following. At this point, I cleaned up all the greifing, but left for a new 
#- town. Maybe someday it'll be safe to come back. If you want the coords, just ask.


#- 